    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>A nonmagical weapon you touch becomes a magic weapon. Choose one of the following damage types: acid, cold, fire, lightning, or thunder. For the duration, the weapon has a +1 bonus to attack rolls and deals an extra [[/damage 1d4]] damage of the chosen type when it hits.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p></p><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"At Higher Levels\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 5th or 6th level, the bonus to attack rolls increases to +2 and the extra damage increases to [[/damage 2d4]]. When you use a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the bonus increases to +3 and the extra damage increases to [[/damage 3d4]].</p></div></div>",
